{"tid":212489,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【科技籽】女子電競職業化　港女組隊戰《英雄聯盟》","createTime":"2017-04-22T12:56:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-22T13:42:13.000Z","uid":30561,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c705bad08bcedfb947e0a4315be64b6f614f0c8b","tid":212489,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T12:56:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20170419/large/19fu601p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20170419%2Flarge%2F19fu601p.jpg&h=2ae09ddf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【科技籽：玩物達人】<br />\n旅發局計劃今年8月搞電子競技嘉年華，電競在香港似乎有上位之勢。中國頂級男子選手打比賽做直播、年薪過百萬，這股電競風近年吹向女子組，剛於上星期結束的寧波EWG《英雄聯盟》國際電子競技女子大獎賽總獎金達20萬人民幣，最後冠軍由上海LLG戰隊取得，證明電競世界女生也有出頭天，以打機為事業並不是男生專利。<br />\n<br />\n香港也有兩支女子戰隊Panda Cute和Counter Play（CTP）北上競逐大獎賽。Panda Cute是香港首支全職《英雄聯盟》（League of Legends，簡稱LOL）女子電競戰隊（五人為一隊），成員陳嘉靖（Deer）、毛芷晴（Momo）、石凱儀（阿夢）、劉麗芳（LauLau）及嚴雅麗（Lily）先在facebook認識，組隊並參加網吧舉辦的女子電競比賽，後來得經理人賞識在上年12月正式組成職業隊伍。她們受薪全職打機，由前職業選手帶領每天訓練約8小時，也曾到台灣與周杰倫做老闆的電競隊J Team集訓。<br />\n今年3月本地電競組織CGA舉辦了「SHERO英雄聯盟國際女子邀請賽」，Panda Cute以不敗姿態取得香港區冠軍，最後惜敗於台灣隊伍。這次以受邀外國隊伍身份參加EWG，隊長Deer知道是越級挑戰，「始終我們是比較新的戰隊，大陸的職業隊全部都很有經驗。」另一支隊伍Counter Play則由毛記電視主播「佘驚曼」游敏擔任隊長，本身愛好LOL的她找來其他YouTuber和女機迷組隊，於3月匆忙成軍，跟Panda Cute一樣找來前職業選手當教練，游敏和隊友表示：「未有當全職選手的打算，但備戰期間和全職的訓練差不多，日練約8小時。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/supplement/tech/art/20170419/19993709\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fsupplement%2Ftech%2Fart%2F20170419%2F19993709&d=jSYRdVihxMCX8m9Ry8wFHe9M5Ue6CDmcYDZznX2R1Ws%3D&h=4ae6c3f3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fsupplement%2Ftech%2Fart%2F20170419%2F19993709&h=8bb915da\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/supplement/tech/art/20170419/19993709</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20170419/large/19fu606p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20170419%2Flarge%2F19fu606p.jpg&h=4e81f016&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20170419/large/19fu603p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20170419%2Flarge%2F19fu603p.jpg&h=0416b559&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9a42560af4bc2c6d02e8ede150a157d3bf573372","tid":212489,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T13:42:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}